## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Extending the MongoDB Schema**: We are adding `completedTopics` (array), `goldMastery` (array), and `coins` (number) fields to the existing `User` model, and creating a new `StudentAttemptLog` collection for attempt logging.
>
> **Soft Fallback for Guest Mode**: If MongoDB is disconnected or if the student plays as a guest (without logging in), progress will be saved/retrieved in/from `localStorage` (e.g. `tenali-completed-topics`, `tenali-gold-mastery`, `tenali-coins`). This ensures the app works in all local/production environments.

